# LifeLine needs NO API keys, NO credits, NO accounts. There is nothing to fill in.
# This file documents the single optional knob:
#
#   LIFELINE_OFFLINE=1   force the bundled offline demo set for every channel
#                        (guaranteed-safe stage demo / CI; default is live sources)
#
# Leave unset for normal operation — LifeLine hits real public sources directly
# and falls back to the offline set automatically if any source is unreachable.
